model

Class ProjectManagementService

  • java.lang.Object
    • model.ProjectManagementService

  • public class ProjectManagementService
extends java.lang.Object
    The ProjectManagementService class manages operations related to projects within the system. It handles the creation, update, deletion, and querying of projects, as well as managing associated data gatherers and their contributions to specific projects.
